metadata.name: RockArt #1 Kurt Cobain, Nirvana
metadata.description:
RockArt is a collection of 222 NFTs of most iconic and famous musicians who left a great legacy in history of rock music.
RockArt #1 is a generated digital artwork and bright physical painting on canvas with typographic printing technique and maximum colour change.
The winning bidder or buyer will receive the physical painting on canvas with shipping included!
Edition: 1 of 1
